c: 3
v: 81
t: "So God accepted an agreement from the prophets: \"Have I not given you some of a Book plus wisdom?\" Then a messenger came to you to confirm what you already had, so you might believe in him and support him. He said: \"Have you acknowledged and accepted that obligation of mine?\" They said: ´We so acknowledge it.\" He said: \"Then act as witnesses; I am one of those testifying along with you"